data.description: This Completely Renovated Colonial Is Truly A Work Of Art. This Magnificent 5 Bedroom, 3 Full Bathroom Home Really Has It All From Professional Craftsmanship To Pronounced Efficiency. This Elegant Home is 2500 Square Feet Plus a Full Finished Basement. There Is An Attached Garage That Has The Electrical Hookup Readily Available For Any Electric Car Charger That You Would Like. The First Floor Has A Formal Dining Room, Living Room, Kitchen With Brand New SS Appliances And An Eat In Kitchen Space, As Well As 1 Bedroom. The Second Floor Has 4 Bedrooms Which Includes A Master Suite With A Full Bathroom And Walk In Closet. The Second Floor Also Has A Hallway Laundry Closet Fully Equipped With Brand New Washer And Dryer Set. This Home Wont Last! This Property Is Flood Zone X, No Flood Insurance Required.
